==Swedish==
===Noun===

:''indef. form''  |  50-öring  |  50-öringar
:''def. form''    | 50-öringen | 50-öringarna

# A swedish coin with nominal value 50 [[öre]], and the smallest coin in use in Sweden. As of June 2004, it was worth approximately 6 US-cents.

